OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'I change how I look and   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftalk to fit in at work'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "I do notice that I'm not being myself 
OL,6, in the workplace," says Hilda Kwoffie. 
OL,7, "I try to tone it down a little bit.   
OL,8, You find yourself having to always     
OL,9, slick your hair down just to fit in."  
OL,11,FThe 24-year-old from Ghana says she's  
OL,12,Fchanged her look and the way she talks 
OL,13,Fsince moving to the UK in 2016.        
OL,15,FTwo-thirds of women of colour in UK    
OL,16,Fworkplaces say they change themselves  
OL,17,Fto fit in, according to a new report.  
OL,19,FThe government said all workplaces     
OL,20,Fshould be free of discrimination.      
